</ol>
```

---

### ✅ Notes

- This is a **simplified** Markdown parser. For full Markdown support, consider using a library like [markdown.cpp](https://github.com/jbeder/markdown) or [pugixml](https://github.com/zeux/pugixml).
- The function is **not thread-safe** and is intended for **simple use cases**.
- You can extend this function to support more Markdown features like links, images, code blocks, etc.

